('Yale University', 'yale', 'New Haven', 'CT', 'private_nonprofit', 4.35, 1530, 34, 100, 7.0, 62250, 62250, 62250, 18450, 80700, 56000, true, false, true, true, 14776, 12.3, '6:1', ARRAY['Economics','Political Science','History','Biology','Computer Science'], 'urban', 'https://www.yale.edu', 'Yale is need-blind for international students and meets 100% of demonstrated need. Strong liberal arts focus with world-class resources. Over 65% of students receive financial aid.', 5),
